function Agg = Modified_Borda_Aggregation(Str,outpath)                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  
if isdir(outpath)
    a = dir(fullfile(outpath,['*' Str '*']));
else
    error('Invalid directory name.');
end
load(fullfile(outpath,a(1).name));
L = numel(Adj_Matrix);

func = 1./[1:L].^2;
accumulator = zeros(L,1);
for i = 1:length(a)
    accumulatee = zeros(L,1);
    load(fullfile(outpath,a(i).name));                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              
    ranking_vector = reshape(abs(Adj_Matrix),L,1);
    [sorted_vector,sorted_inds] = sort(ranking_vector,'descend');
    accumulatee(sorted_inds) = func';
    accumulator = accumulator + accumulatee.*(ranking_vector~=0);
end
Agg = reshape(accumulator,size(Adj_Matrix,1),size(Adj_Matrix,2));
for i = 1:size(Agg,1)
    Agg(i,i) = 0;
end